h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Battlefield is Never the Same</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level layouts shift, enemy positions change. Adapt or die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698460/extras/7afbbbd46a1563596fca814b5f785714.poster.avif?t=1755213162\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698460/extras/7afbbbd46a1563596fca814b5f785714.webm?t=1755213162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698460/extras/7afbbbd46a1563596fca814b5f785714.mp4?t=1755213162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready? Then shatter the loop, crush your enemies, and rip reality apart.</strong></p>",
